OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers only
OL,6,Fslowly easing overnight, however
OL,7,Feastern areas should become mostly dry
OL,8,Fby dawn. A brisk breeze continuing
OL,9,Fovernight, with temperatures on the
OL,10,Fmild side.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FFurther scattered showers,
OL,13,Fwith patchy rain at times across the
OL,14,FPennines. Best chance of brighter
OL,15,Fspells in the east. A brisk breeze but
OL,16,Ffeeling milder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
