OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FThursday, cloud and rain easing north
OL,7,Fthen drier, warmer. Friday, warm with
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells. Chance of
OL,9,Fthundery evening showers. Saturday,
OL,10,Fwarm with bright spells, thundery
OL,11,Fshowers still possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
